  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hop to It</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721680/extras/58aec70266dd3711707eae3d95c8c768.poster.avif?t=1771657068\" width=588 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721680/extras/58aec70266dd3711707eae3d95c8c768.webm?t=1771657068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721680/extras/58aec70266dd3711707eae3d95c8c768.mp4?t=1771657068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Jump, swerve, and jump again through simple but tricky stages that'll test your aim, control, and perception. Will you and Ball take the journey on 'Normal' mode for a fun challenge, or are you both willing to risk it for the biscuit with 'Baller' mode's aggressive timer and faster platforms?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bop to it</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721680/extras/ecb52dd1d464354bfe49338e01b7ea12.poster.avif?t=1771657068\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721680/extras/ecb52dd1d464354bfe49338e01b7ea12.webm?t=1771657068\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721680/extras/ecb52dd1d464354bfe49338e01b7ea12.mp4?t=1771657068\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bounce to the beat of a groovy hip-hop and lo-fi soundtrack while you and Ball seek out a silly, yet thoughtful collection of balls.",
